# Epic 2: Backend API Scaffolding
**Status:** Depends on Epic 1 | **Arch Ref:** Section 4.1 (Dual-Port)

## Technical Blueprint
- **Framework:** Python Flask (Pure JSON).
- **Ports:** Port 5000 (App Traffic) and Port 8081 (Metrics/Admin).
- **Standards:** Every response must be `application/json`.

## Stories & Specs
### 2.1 Dual-Port Listener
- **Action:** Initialize Flask. Implement logic to run listeners on 5000 and 8081 simultaneously.
- **AC:** App is accessible on both ports.

### 2.2 Base API Routes
- **Action:** Create `backend/src/app.py`. Implement `/api/health`.
- **AC:** Returns `{"status": "up"}` with 200 OK.
